Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.45,0:00:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天的课堂就到這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.45,0:00:30.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老师再见\N回家路上小心喔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.61,0:00:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好累啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.66,0:00:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是這所學校的老师 櫻心美
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.81,0:00:57.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然大家都評價我是一位热心教育\N為学生著想的老师
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.53,0:01:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是放学後的鈴聲响起 \N另一个我就全面展現了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.73,0:01:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.36,0:01:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,櫻老师
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.93,0:01:48.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老师的真的很守時啊\N馬上开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.57,0:01:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給我拿來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.16,0:02:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是還是不要做這樣的事情比较好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.61,0:02:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.41,0:02:22.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,與其說是作为教师 不如說是這所學校吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.03,0:02:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這所学校里做這樣的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.38,0:02:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老师 正是因为有新鲜感才會興奮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.95,0:02:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,櫻老師
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.59,0:02:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把煩惱都忘掉吧 像平常一樣享受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.07,0:03:27.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看 你喜歡這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.29,0:03:33.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.05,0:04:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想要口水嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.04,0:04:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,口水嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.06,0:04:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.02,0:04:47.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.72,0:04:52.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好美味\N繼續吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.96,0:05:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來摸我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.97,0:05:34.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.82,0:05:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.29,0:06:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再多摸一點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.39,0:06:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想直接摸嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.89,0:06:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好想摸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.23,0:07:01.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.64,0:07:34.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.08,0:07:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想舔屁股嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.14,0:07:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師 好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.48,0:07:53.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看得見嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.23,0:07:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舔我屁股吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.21,0:08:03.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.80,0:08:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.22,0:08:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了 舔那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.53,0:08:37.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.15,0:08:41.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.16,0:09:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,更多
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.96,0:09:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.92,0:09:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.84,0:09:45.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這邊也來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.11,0:09:48.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好濕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.92,0:09:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,更多
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.36,0:10:10.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.84,0:10:23.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高潮了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.82,0:10:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.91,0:10:43.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡嗎 \N再深一點
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.81,0:10:55.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師好美啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.67,0:10:59.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.19,0:11:02.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再繼續
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.28,0:11:08.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.94,0:11:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再深入一點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.50,0:11:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高潮了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.80,0:11:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.53,0:11:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,繼續
